function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
	--Get the follower and move to position for meshif conversation
	idLorathFollower = Hydra.QuestGetFollower("NPC_QST_Lorath_Follower")
	Hydra.ActorClearAnimSetOverride(idLorathFollower)
	Hydra.QuestFollowerTakeOwnership(idLorathFollower)
	
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idLorathFollower, OASIS_LORATH, "NPC_Walk_Fast", true, false, true, true)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(idLorathFollower, OASIS_LORATH)
	Hydra.QActorSheath(idLorathFollower)
	Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(idLorathFollower)
	Hydra.ActorDelete(idLorathFollower)
	Hydra.ActorEnable(OASIS_LORATH)
	
	Hydra.QActorAnim(OASIS_LORATH, "AnimKey_evnt_kickChest")
	Hydra.Wait(1.2)
	Hydra.QActorSetAnimSetOverride(OASIS_MESHIF, S_MESHIF_WAKEUP_ANIMSET)
	


end

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)
--	-- barman is like what are you doing back there?
	
	Hydra.QActorClearAnimSetOverride(OASIS_BAR_BANDIT_01)
	Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(OASIS_BAR_BANDIT_01, 0.5)
	Hydra.QActorClearAnimSetOverride(OASIS_BAR_BANDIT_02)
	Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(OASIS_BAR_BANDIT_02, 0.5)
	Hydra.QActorClearAnimSetOverride(OASIS_BAR_BANDIT_03)
	Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(OASIS_BAR_BANDIT_03, 0.5)
	Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(OASIS_BAR_BANDIT_01)
	Hydra.ActorEnable(OASIS_COMBAT_BANDIT_01)
	Hydra.ActorEnable(OASIS_COMBAT_BANDIT_02)
	Hydra.ActorEnable(OASIS_COMBAT_BANDIT_03)
	
	-- activate the bar fight
	for i, ActorID in ipairs(GROUP_BANDITS_TAVERN) do
		Hydra.ActorClearAnimSetOverride(ActorID)
		Hydra.ActorEnableAI(ActorID, true)
		Hydra.ActorSetTeam(ActorID, Hydra.TEAM_MONSTER_DEFAULT)
		Hydra.ActorAIForcePrimaryTarget(ActorID, idActorPlayer)
	end
	
	-- Move exterior bandits to inside the bar
	for i, ActorID in ipairs(GROUP_BANDITS_TENT) do
		Hydra.ActorSetAITether(ActorID, OASIS_TAVERN_DOOR_MARKER)
		Hydra.Wait(0.1)
	end
end
